    <testcase name="test_cargo_build_release" classname="true_e2e::cargo" time="8.45">
      <failure message="Artifact hash mismatch">
Expected: abc123...
Actual: def456...
      </failure>
    </testcase>
    <testcase name="test_cargo_test_all_pass" classname="true_e2e::cargo" time="12.34">
      <skipped message="No workers available"/>
    </testcase>
  </testsuite>
</testsuites>
```

### 2. HTML Report (report.html)
Visual report with:
- Summary table (pass/fail/skip counts)
- Test list with expandable details
- Timing chart (bar graph of test durations)
- Failure details with log excerpts
- Worker utilization stats

